    <p><strong>Parts logistics:</strong> OEM Kalamazoo parts ship from Kalamazoo, Michigan. Typical turn 5 to 10 business days. We always quote total turn time honestly: diagnosis day, parts ship time, return-visit install. No 24-hour-fix promises we can't deliver.</p>
